# Nyarch Tour QT

A KDE Kirigami-based version of Nyarch Tour for Nyarch Linux.

Built with Python (PySide6) and Kirigami for native KDE Plasma integration.

## Features

- Carousel-style tour pages
- One-click launch buttons for featured apps/tools
- Conditional Timeshift page on BTRFS systems
- Early-exit confirmation dialog (same behavior as GTK tour)

## App ID

`moe.nyarchlinux.tourqt`

## Local development

```bash
python3 -m venv --system-site-packages env
source env/bin/activate
pip install --editable .
nyarchtourqt
```

## Flatpak build

Install runtime dependencies:

```bash
flatpak install flathub org.kde.Platform//6.8 org.kde.Sdk//6.8 io.qt.PySide.BaseApp//6.8
```

Build and run:

```bash
flatpak-builder --force-clean --install-deps-from flathub flatpak-build-dir moe.nyarchlinux.tourqt.json
flatpak-builder --run flatpak-build-dir moe.nyarchlinux.tourqt.json nyarchtourqt
```

